== Prequisites

* Java 1.6+
* MongoDB 2+

== Configure

Comy supports Replica Set, see:
http://www.mongodb.org/display/DOCS/Replica+Sets

Edit config.properties to suit your environment. You may also need to edit
http.sh to change the JVM memory option.

== Run

bin/runner.sh comy.Boot

== Remove old data

You may need to remove URL entries that are not accessed for a long time:
bin/runner.sh comy.GC

You may need to the command to be run periodically.
